{"tid":46211,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴絲想3月底前去澳洲？？","createTime":"2016-12-19T13:28:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-01T12:11:52.000Z","uid":52966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a973b5ae4d88c6d5bd0dcd226491926e41e6abf4","tid":46211,"uid":52966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T13:28:36.000Z","msg":"幫Ar哥Ar嫂放2人Sydney 5D4N package<br />\n原本Ar哥Ar嫂打算3月去<br />\n但剛剛驗到有咗BB<br />\n唔方便去<br />\n有冇巴絲3月底前想去又未買package?<br />\n佢地想15K放<br />\n(價錢可以再議）<br />\n當幫補下奶粉錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\npackage係5D4N<br />\n搭國泰<br />\n住breakfree on george<br />\n可以另加錢stay多幾日 or 轉其他酒店<br />\n到下年3月底到期<br />\n但12月18 -  下年1月2 &amp; 1月26  - 31用唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇下有冇巴絲有興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"700056a6476cf90c330eae08a9b80020cea253f0","tid":46211,"uid":52966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T13:30:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5e4688b48908b391527e3d3df29a12f04e660ca","tid":46211,"uid":52966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T13:38:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"048643dd9755d8e9fe739e03cc92a9962ad2099b","tid":46211,"uid":52966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T13:47:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a52a93eeb4660566fd291b6526d5d5ac6c8c1147","tid":46211,"uid":52966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T16:02:54.000Z","msg":"<